        <p>Marathon runners who consumed tart cherry extract experienced 13-23% less muscle soreness (DOMS) and recovered strength 12% faster than placebo groups. Tart cherry reduces exercise-induced oxidative stress by neutralizing free radicals generated during intense physical activity.</p>
      </div>
